Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: This single story office building is located in Stony Brook. The building is equipped with a backup generator in place, excellent parking and quick access to Hurstbourne Parkway and to I-64. In addition, this building also has a dock available for a flex user. There is currently 5,500  square feet of available space.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Class A Office Space in Mized-Use Development
